webpackJsonp([0xb4589a32f2eb],{448:function(e,n){e.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"jasperjn's blog",author:"jasperjn",disqus:"jasperjn"}},markdownRemark:{id:"/home/circleci/repo/content/_posts/2017-07-17-chrome-build-in-screenshot/index.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark",html:'<p>Chrome 59 DevTools 中釋出 Full-page screenshots，不用額外安裝擴充功能或截圖軟體，直接使用內建的截圖功能擷取網頁畫面。</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<h2>Full-page screenshots 使用方法</h2>\n<p>DevTools 提供了兩種 \b 截圖方式。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Capture screenshot：擷取可視區域 (viewport)。</li>\n<li>Capture full size screenshot：擷取整個網頁 \b。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>使用步驟</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>點選左下角的 Toggle device toolbar。</li>\n<li>\b 點選右上角的 More options。</li>\n<li>Capture screenshot：擷取可視區域。</li>\n<li>Capture full size screenshot：擷取整個網頁。</li>\n</ol>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-1e188.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 85.3852967227635%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Full-page screenshots 使用方法"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-fb8a0.png"\n        srcset="/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-526de.png 885w,\n/static/screenshot-steps-d48b89e47f54bcd48c3f9eb325c06f42-1e188.png 1129w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>也可以直接透過 Command Menu (<kbd>cmd</kbd>+<kbd>shift</kbd>+<kbd>p</kbd>) 搜尋關鍵字 screenshot \b 執行截圖功能，不需開啟 device toolbar。\n\b\n\n  <a\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-link"\n    href="/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-d6552.png"\n    style="display: block"\n    target="_blank"\n    rel="noopener"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"\n    style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"\n  >\n    <span\n      class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image"\n      style="padding-bottom: 93.89558232931726%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(\'data:image/png;base64,\'); background-size: cover; display: block;"\n    >\n      <img\n        class="gatsby-resp-image-image"\n        style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;"\n        alt="Command Menu screenshot"\n        title=""\n        src="/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-fb8a0.png"\n        srcset="/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-526de.png 885w,\n/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/command-menu-screenshot-895ad85302104a9d1d0040cc1db80337-d6552.png 1245w"\n        sizes="(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>完整的操作方式可以參考 \b 官方的影片：</p>\n<div>\n          <div\n            class="gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper"\n            style="padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden;margin-bottom: 1.0725rem"\n          >\n            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r_6_9eFPhxI" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen style="\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n          "></iframe>\n          </div>\n          </div>\n<h2>參考資料</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://developers.google.com/web/updates/2017/04/devtools-release-notes">What’s New In DevTools (Chrome 59)</a></li>\n</ul>',frontmatter:{title:"使用 Chrome 內建截圖工具擷取網頁畫面",date:"July 17, 2017",tags:["chrome"]}}},pathContext:{slug:"/2017/07/17/chrome-build-in-screenshot/",previous:{fields:{slug:"/2017/05/11/cannot-install-extensions-on-vscode/"},frontmatter:{title:"VScode 無法安裝擴充功能",tags:["vscode"]}},next:{fields:{slug:"/2017/10/27/google-cloud-platform/"},frontmatter:{title:"使用 Google Cloud Platform 建立 Node.js 網站",tags:["google cloud platform","google cloud sdk","app engine","gcp"]}}}}}});
